<task id="R3-025" project="spaarke-platform-foundations-r3">
  <metadata>
    <title>Integration tests for admin endpoints + scheduler migration</title>
    <status>completed</status>
    <completion-date>2026-06-21</completion-date>
    <completion-notes>
28 new integration tests added; all pass. Two test files authored:
(1) tests/integration/Sprk.Bff.Api.IntegrationTests/Admin/JobsEndpointsTests.cs — 15 tests
    via WebApplicationFactory&lt;Program&gt; against the full BFF bootstrap + production
    SystemAdmin policy + real SchedulingModule DI graph. Covers AC-2.1 (discovery),
    AC-2.3 (status + manual trigger with 202+Location+TriggerResponse), AC-2.5 (Theory:
    6 endpoints × non-admin → 403 AND unauthenticated → 401 — total 12 theory rows),
    AC-2.6 (enable/disable flip + correlationId on run records), AC-2.7 (failed-job
    error surfacing via /status). Includes dedicated AdminJobsIntegrationFixture
    mirroring the canonical configuration-key set from DataverseIntegrationTestFixture
    so all Program.cs option validators pass (per test-fixture-contracts.md §F.2).
(2) tests/integration/Sprk.Bff.Api.IntegrationTests/Scheduling/PlaybookSchedulerJobTests.cs
    — 13 tests driving PlaybookSchedulerJob.ExecuteAsync directly against in-memory
    FakeGenericEntityService + FakePlaybookOrchestrationService wired through a real
    IServiceProvider (no WebApplicationFactory needed — the job is a pure
    IScheduledJob handler). Covers AC-2.4 fan-out (7 playbooks single-row), AC-2.4
    cadence preservation (Theory: 6 boundary rows + 1 full-tick test mixing hourly/
    daily/weekly playbooks), Q1 fresh correlationId per child (uniqueness AND distinct
    from parent), AC-2.4 sprk_lastrundate advancement.

Hard constraints honored: no production code modified (test-only), no .claude/ paths
touched, no new NuGet packages added (no CVE delta possible), in-memory fakes used
throughout (no live Dataverse / SB needed). Test-update obligation per
bff-extensions.md §F-test-update-obligation satisfied for tasks 020-024 deliverables.

Coverage complements the in-process unit-flavored tests at
tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/Api/Admin/JobsEndpointsTests.cs (~30 tests) without
duplication — the integration suite focuses on headline AC paths through full
production wiring; the unit suite covers exhaustive 4xx/5xx + edge cases.
    </completion-notes>
